openbus-0.0.1-cluster01.json

    Cluster with name "cluster01" with:

        1. Batch Layer (Hadoop)
        2. Bus Layer (Kafka)
        3. Speed Layer -> Storm
        4. Serving Layer -> HBase on top of Batch Layer.

openbus-0.0.1-cluster02.json

Cluster with name "cluster02" with:

        1. Batch Layer (Hadoop)
        2. Bus Layer (Kafka)
        3. Speed Layer -> Storm
        4. Serving Layer -> ElasticSearch on top of Batch Layer.


openbus-0.0.1-cluster03.json

Cluster with name "cluster02" with:

        1. Batch Layer (Hadoop)
        2. Bus Layer (Kafka)
        3. Speed Layer -> Storm
        4. Serving Layer -> Cassandra with dedicated cluster.


